name: UKCoreAllergyManifestation
title: UK Core Allergy Manifestation
description: A set of codes that describe how a patient's allergy was manifested. Selected from the 'Health issues' simple reference set of the SNOMED CT UK coding system.  Alternatively provides a code indicating a degrade of information about a clinical record entry.
